## mem 
# text "mem"
${voffset 151}${offset 92}${font Ubuntu:size=10,weight:bold}${color5}MEM
# ram percentage
${voffset -30}${offset 50}${font sawasdee:size=15,weight:bold}${color5}${memperc}${font sawasdee:size=9,weight:bold}%
